          {
            "element_id": "33455908",
            "value": "Toushini continues to be a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in her speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. During this marking period, she also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive her results, including her updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455911",
            "value": "Toushini is a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing. We are currently focusing on developing her grammar skills and supporting smoother transitions between activities and class routines. I am proud of her efforts and look forward to supporting her continued growth throughout the year!"
          },
