          {
            "element_id": "33455908",
            "value": "Aaron successfully completed WIDA ACCESS testing during the months of January and February. Results of the test will be sent home in the late Spring of 2026. Aaron reviews classroom expectations before and after every class using a list he created. Aaron desires to be successful and is an active participator in class discussions."
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455911",
            "value": "Aaron benefits from adult support during transitions and group activities. He needs reminders to respect the personal space of others during rug and group activities. Aaron has many good skills which he successfully shares when working independently or 1-1 with the teacher. He is well liked among his peers and is a great helper when asked to assist others with their work."
