          {
            "element_id": "33455908",
            "value": "Elisa continues to be a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in her speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills, and her hard work is evident each day. During this marking period, she also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive her results, including her updated English proficiency levels, in June. I am proud of Elisa's ongoing efforts and look forward to supporting her continued growth throughout the year!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455911",
            "value": "Elisa is a pleasure to have in class. She is making great progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing. In writing, we are currently working on breaking up long sentences into smaller, complete sentences. I am proud of her efforts and look forward to supporting her continued growth throughout the year!"
