          {
            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "Arjun continues to be a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in his speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. During this marking period, he also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive his results, including his updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455558",
            "value": "Arjun is a pleasure to have in class! He enjoys being part of the group in ELD and does a great job following directions and participating in activities. It has been wonderful to see him speaking more often and engaging with his peers. I am proud of his progress and look forward to supporting his continued growth throughout the year!"
