          {
            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "Taeoh continues to be a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in his speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills, and his hard work is evident each day. During this marking period, he also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive his results, including his updated English proficiency levels, in June. I am proud of Taeoh's ongoing efforts and look forward to supporting his continued growth throughout the year!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455558",
            "value": "Taeoh is a pleasure to have in class. He has made steady progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing, and his proficiency is developing well. We are continuing to work on strengthening his writing skills and reinforcing the importance of following directions and meeting classroom expectations. I am proud of his efforts and look forward to supporting his continued growth throughout the year!"
