          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "Olivia successfully completed WIDA ACCESS testing during the months of January and February. Results of the test will be sent home in the late Spring of 2026.Olivia works well when 1-1 with an adult. It is more challenging for Olivia to maintain focus and follow directions when working within a group of students. Olivia will be receiving extra 1-1 ELD instruction 3 times a cycle starting in the 3rd MP to assist with spelling, writing and comprehension of both oral and written information."
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455558",
            "value": "Olivia is a good helper to other Chinese speaking students in our class. Olivia works diligently in a one to one setting where she can receive adult support to assist with interpreting WH questions and decoding longer words as well as editing written work. Olivia enjoys class activities but benefits from reminders to follow directions and complete her assignments as expected. It is exciting to see how much Olivia has grown in her confidence and skills since starting at VFES last year!"
          },
