          {
            "element_id": "33455908",
            "value": "Heman continues to be a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in his speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. During this marking period, he also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive his results, including his updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
