          {
            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "Selen continues to be a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in her speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills, and her hard work is evident each day. During this marking period, she also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive her results, including her updated English proficiency levels, in June. I am proud of Selen's ongoing efforts and look forward to supporting her continued growth throughout the year!"
          },
