          {
            "element_id": "33453672",
            "value": "Prabhav continues make excellent progress in his speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. We are continuing to work on treating others with kindness and in taking responsibility and being honest in challenging moments. During this marking period, he also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive his results, including his updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33453675",
            "value": "Prabhav is a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing. I am proud of his efforts and look forward to supporting his continued growth throughout the year!"
