            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "Mika continues to be a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in his speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills, and his hard work is evident each day. During this marking period, he also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive his results, including his updated English proficiency levels, in June. I am proud of Mika's ongoing efforts and look forward to supporting his continued growth throughout the year!"
