          {
            "element_id": "33453672",
            "value": "Siddhaarth continues to be a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in his speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. During this marking period, he also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive his results, including his updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33453675",
            "value": "Siddhaarth is a pleasure to have in class. He is making steady progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing. While he occasionally struggles with self-control at times, he is learning strategies to manage these moments. I am proud of his efforts and look forward to supporting his continued growth throughout the year!"
