          {
            "element_id": "33453672",
            "value": "Hetvika continues to be a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in her speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. During this marking period, she also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive her results, including her updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33453675",
            "value": "Hetvika is a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing. She is continuing to develop her ability to stay focused and complete tasks more efficiently. With support and practice, I am confident she will keep growing in these areas. I am proud of her efforts and look forward to her continued success throughout the year!"
