          {
            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "Aizuura continues to be a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in her speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. Aizuura continues to benefit from additional support in reading and writing. During this marking period, she also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive her results, including her updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
          },
          {
            "element_id": "33455558",
            "value": "Aizuura is a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in speaking, listening, reading, and writing, and her proficiency continues to develop well. We are working on strengthening her writing skills and reinforcing the importance of following directions, classroom expectations, and smooth transitions. Aizuura also benefits from additional support in reading and writing. I am proud of her efforts and look forward to supporting her continued growth throughout the year!"
