          {
            "element_id": "33455555",
            "value": "We were so happy to welcome Chaanvika to Devon during this marking period! She is a pleasure to have in class. She is making steady progress in her speaking, listening, reading, and writing skills. During this marking period, she also completed the WIDA ACCESS assessment. We will receive her results, including her updated English proficiency levels, in June. Keep up the good work!"
