            "value": "Bozhi is most successful in class when working 1-1 with the ELD teacher. Using a personalized visual schedule and implementing breaks is beginning to help Bozhi learn what is expected of him in school. All work in the ELD classroom has been differentiated to best meet his needs at this time.\nBozhi successfully completed WIDA ACCESS testing during the months of January and February. Results of the test will be sent home in the late Spring of 2026."
