          {
            "element_id": "33455908",
            "value": "Sejun joined our class in January and is continuing to adjust well to his new school environment. As he is currently at an English proficiency level of 1.0, we are not yet able to fully evaluate his instructional skills across academic domains. At this time, he is working on foundational English literacy skills through Orton–Gillingham lessons, with a focus on letter–sound relationships, phonological awareness, and early decoding. He is demonstrating steady engagement during lessons and is beginning to develop confidence as he learns to read in English. As his English skills continue to grow, we look forward to gaining a clearer picture of his academic abilities. It is a pleasure working with him, and we are encouraged by his positive attitude and effort.&nbsp;"
